{
  "stem": "1753.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were done away with.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So once again, this tall, elderly SS man, by the name of Untersturmfuhrer Pravey from Kaiserslautern in Germany, which we knew, selected to stay with Taup and me to become water carriers, which probably was the best job in the entire camp.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The water carrier-- I don't know why he selected me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I looked young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I looked fit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe he could sense because I spoke German he could converse with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe I looked-- I-- I had a little life in me, and that's what he really needed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The water carriers, there was very little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Treblinka is in an elevated area, maybe a few hundred feet above sea level.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there wasn't all that much water, so naturally, you had to pump the water and dug deep ditches and made--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wells, where the water had to be cranked up with a pail, and then had to be carried over to the guard's kitchen, and to the officer's kitchen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the water was carried-- was pumped in the inner camp, but had to be carried out into the outer camp, as you will see on this map.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the cook was Ukrainian, one was [INAUDIBLE], and the other one was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He liked us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we always put some leftovers under the pail as we went back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there were 550 that somehow, because no new transports came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So for the next 11 and a half months, tranquility existed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So who were the 550 people?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The professionals, the carpenters, the blacksmiths, the tinsmiths, the tailors, the cooks, the electricians, whoever could perform some work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The group that had got used to work the water carriers, like myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why did they need so many?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
